description: For sale: $259,000. If you are looking for complete privacy surrounded by woods with a quality built cabin this is the place! One of a kind hunting property on 140 acres of great variety of land: from lake & river frontage to high & low ground excellent for wildlife. Seller maintains a nice trail system throughout all 4 parcels with pretty fancy heated deer stands. Home built in 2005 and has 3 cozy Bdrm, 3/4 Ba + half Ba. Open floor plan, custom made kitchen cabinets & furniture. Thermostatically controlled gas fire place provides the heat. You will enjoy spending time in the 3 season porch & outside by the fire pit area. Newer propane Generac generator provides power. You'll have drilled well & holding septic tank.  Beautiful pond is within view of the cabin. Property is surrounded on all sides by a public state land (Kettle Lake Wildlife management area). Kettle lake public access is down the road and it's a dead end road. Kettle lake is an environmental lake. There is not physical access to the lake from the property. You would want to use the public lake access. It's a wildlife paradise out there! You can hunt white tail deer, waterfowl, grouse. Fish from the river as well. You have to come see it to appreciate everything this property offers! Set up your private showing today or call with any questions!

description: Recently sold: $212,400. Move-in ready Contemporary Chalet located on Upper (North) Island!  Year-round home or cabin resting on a nice lot, offers room to play & enjoy.
